{"tid":1346743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非當地居民同我入黎記熟所有大學避難所","createTime":"2019-07-22T04:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:57:25.000Z","uid":51200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b515b075fde7e9b3a216f3b3263419134010193a","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"每逢有啲咩社會大事<br />\n大學學生會一定會開放庇護所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［size=5]屯門天水圍元朗區[/size=5]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【嶺南大學開放庇護站】<br />\n嶺南大學康樂樓2樓屬於學生會管理，現開放2樓空地予有需要人士暫作休息，避免受不必要滋擾及攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n地址：屯門青山公路嶺南段8號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請不要逗留在元朗站，直接由兆康站前往嶺南，並於北閘進入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">九龍區</span><br />\n<br />\n【城大學生會現開放休息中心】<br />\n<br />\n學生會現開放位中國銀行香港綜合樓7樓之R7200室作休息中心，同學若有需要可前往稍作休息或簡單處理傷口。<br />\n<br />\n【香港浸會大學學生會臨時庇護中心開放】<br />\n<br />\n本會舊校學生會室YSS501會開放供同學作休息留宿及更換衣服之用。敬請同學注意人身安全，有任何需要及有關詳情請聯絡幹事 王沐恩 tel:6110 3860。<br />\n<br />\nRoom 501, Yeung Shui Sang Building, Hong Kong Baptist University, 224 Waterloo Road, Kowloon Tong<br />\n<br />\n【理大學生會開放會室】<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會大樓將24小時開放，為支援各遊行行動，開放學生會室予同學作臨時庇護站，並會提供簡單食糧及飲品，如有需要同學可前往稍作休息。<br />\n<br />\n地址：紅磡學生會大樓邵逸夫樓VA329室<br />\n開放時間：至安全為止<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港島區</span><br />\n<br />\n【香港大學學生會臨時庇護中心開放】<br />\n<br />\n敝會已經開放學生會大樓(address: Level UG1, Union Building,<br />\nHKU, Pokfulam, Hong Kong) 予所有需要清洗傷口及休息的同學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大埔區</span><br />\n<br />\n【中大學生會休息中心】<br />\n<br />\n若任何同學需要地方稍作休息（尤其家住元朗者），可前往中大學生會及崇基學生會會室。<br />\n<br />\n地址：中大范克廉樓LG<br />\n            龐萬倫學生活動中心 1樓"},{"pid":"c955b44e7538238e028b581cf1701fc8953bde48","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaddbbba1696096b0c7be7a0275a52fdf873a29","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3407859abe0473d8aebc3d61d9dec4ebc346b2eb","tid":1346743,"uid":237061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"552338fae5798f095e3c165fa24618c4a7c55299","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fed15fe494c28424ae6862382f29a77570963da","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cc7e580286e0addf89e56ad48499942b2f8981","tid":1346743,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}